    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the 13-factor ASME V&V 40 evaluation. The central claim regarding Monte Carlo UQ adequacy is noted as supported by internal evidence documents; however, all seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels and six factors remain unassessed at MRL 5. Despite these gaps, the package is formally accepted at this stage pending remediation plan submission. The claim that Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification adequately bounds hemolysis predictions is recorded as the binding claim for this assurance package.",
